title: Gat seng gung ziu aka The Fun, the Luck & the Tycoon
description:
This early To film stars Chow Yun Fat and Sylvia Chang in a frothy comedy that captures the 1980s in all its excessive, materialistic glory. Lam Bo Sun, the richest man in Hong Kong, is expected to marry the ditziest of socialites in a matter of weeks. On a whim, he leaves everything behind and gets a job as a lowly busboy at a noodle restaurant, and finds the girl of his dreams.
